\test_input{
\: Division and remainder with non-zero remainders for big/big operands.
\: These cover the adjustment branches in div_rem_to_pos_inf, rem_to_pos_inf,
\: div_rem_to_neg_inf, and rem_to_neg_inf.

\: div_to_pos_inf(big+3, big): quotient rounds up from 1 to 2
\cowel_div_to_pos_inf(cowel_add(0x100000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000, 3), 0x100000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000)

\: rem_to_pos_inf(big+3, big): remainder = 3 - big (negative, rounds toward +inf)
\cowel_rem_to_pos_inf(cowel_add(0x100000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000, 3), 0x100000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000)

\: div_to_neg_inf(-(big+3), big): quotient rounds down from -1 to -2
\cowel_div_to_neg_inf(cowel_neg(cowel_add(0x100000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000, 3)), 0x100000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000)

\: rem_to_neg_inf(-(big+3), big): remainder = big - 3 (positive, rounds toward -inf)
\cowel_rem_to_neg_inf(cowel_neg(cowel_add(0x100000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000, 3)), 0x100000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000)
}

